title: Tiangong-1 to be launched in 8 hrs
description: JIUQUAN/BEIJING， Sept. 29 (Xinhua) -- The carrier rocket of Tiangong-1 space lab module， Long March-2FT1， will blast off in eight hours as of 1:16 p.m. Beijing Time (5:16 GMT) Thursday at Jiuquan Satellite Launch Center in northwest China.
cleanContent: JIUQUAN/BEIJING, Sept. 29 (Xinhua) -- The carrier rocket of Tiangong-1 space lab module, Long March-2FT1, will blast off in eight hours as of 1:16 p.m. Beijing Time (5:16 GMT) Thursday at Jiuquan Satellite Launch Center in northwest China.All flight controllers for the Tiangong-1 mission are in position at Beijing Aerospace Flight Control Center.																																																																								|  |
